If European Union data protection law applies to the processing of your personal data, Sanctuary company provides the controls described in the Sanctuary Privacy Policy to let you exercise your right to request an access, update or removal of your information. You have the right to object to the processing of your information or export your information to another service.
What our rights to change the Privacy Policy
Sanctuary reserves the right to amend the Privacy Policy from time to time. Amendments will be effective upon the posting of such updated Privacy Policy at this location or the amended policies or supplemental terms on the applicable Services. Without your consent, Sanctuary will not limit your rights under this Privacy Policy. Your continued access or use of Sanctuary Services after such posting constitutes your consent to be bound by the Privacy Policy, as amended. If you do not agree to the update of the Privacy Policy, please stop using Sanctuary Services.
